quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,41,"niklo, khuwa halkay ho ya boujhal, aur jehaad karo Allah ki raah mein apne malon aur apni jaanun ke sath, yeh tumahray liye behtar hai agar tum jano"
9,42,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, agar faida sehal ul husool hota aur safar halka hota to woh zaroor tumahray peechay chalne par amaada ho jatay, magar un par to yeh rasta bohat kathin ho gaya ab woh khuda ki qasam kha kha kar kahin ge ke agar hum chal satke to yaqeenan tumahray sath chaltay woh apne aap ko halakat mein daal rahay hain Allah khoob jaanta hai ke woh jhutay hain"
9,43,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, Allah tumhe maaf kere, tum ne kyun inhen rukhsat day di? ( tumhe chahiye tha ke khud rukhsat nah dete ) taakay tum par khil jata ke kon log sachey hain aur jhoton ko bhi tum jaan letay"
9,44,jo log Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan rakhtay hain woh to kabhi tum se yeh darkhwast nah karen ge ke inhen apni jaan o maal ke sath jehaad karne se maaf rakha jaye Allah Muttaqiyun ko khoob jaanta hai
9,45,"aisi darkhwasten to sirf wohi log karte hain jo Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan nahi rakhtay, jin ke dilon mein shak hai aur woh apne shak hi mein متردد ho rahay hain"
9,46,"agar waqai un ka iradah niklny ka hota to woh is ke liye kuch tayari karte lekin Allah ko un ka uthna pasand hinah tha, is liye is ne inhen sust kar diya aur keh diya ke baith raho bethnay walon ke sath"
9,47,"agar woh tumahray sath nikaltay to tumahray andar kharabi ke siwa kisi cheez ka izafah nah karte woh tumahray darmain fitnah pardazi ke liye daud dhoop karte, aur tumahray giroh ka haal yeh hai ke abhi uss mein bohat se aisay log mojood hain jo unn ki baatein kaan laga kar suntay hain, Allah inn zaalmon ko khoob jaanta hai"
